com.foreach.across.modules.webcms.data

Class WebCmsDataEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.across.modules.webcms.data.WebCmsDataEntry

  • public final class WebCmsDataEntry
extends Object
    Represents a set of data to be imported. Data should be either a Map or a Collection (usually of Map items).

    0.0.1
    Author:
    Arne Vandamme
    See Also:
